            "id": "https://lollipopazhe.github.io/2021/08/29/Other/markdown/",
            "url": "https://lollipopazhe.github.io/2021/08/29/Other/markdown/",
            "title": "MarkDown文档基本语法",
            "date_published": "2021-08-29T11:44:32.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"markdown文档基本语法\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#markdown文档基本语法\">#</a> MarkDown 文档基本语法</h1>\n<p><ul class=\"toc\">\n<li><a href=\"#markdown%E6%96%87%E6%A1%A3%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E8%AF%AD%E6%B3%95\">MarkDown文档基本语法</a>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%B8%80-%E6%A0%87%E9%A2%98\">一、标题</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BA%8C-%E5%AD%97%E4%BD%93\">二、 字体</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%B8%89-%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\">三、列表</a><br />\n*\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#1%E6%97%A0%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\">1.无序列表</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#2%E6%9C%89%E5%BA%8F%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8\">2.有序列表</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#3%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8%E5%B5%8C%E5%A5%97\">3.列表嵌套</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%9B%9B-%E5%88%86%E5%89%B2%E7%BA%BF\">四、分割线</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%BA%94-%E5%BC%95%E7%94%A8\">五、 引用</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%85%AD-%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87\">六、 图片</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%B8%83-%E8%A1%A8%E6%A0%BC\">七、 表格</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%85%AB-%E4%BB%A3%E7%A0%81%E5%9D%97\">八、 代码块</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E4%B9%9D-%E8%B6%85%E9%93%BE%E6%8E%A5\">九、 超链接</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%8D%81-%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95\">十、 目录</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%80-%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96\">十一、 其他</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</p>\n<h2 id=\"一-标题\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#一-标题\">#</a> 一、标题</h2>\n<p><strong>“#” 表示标题，几个 “#” 代表几级标题，最多六级：</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre># 一级标题</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>## 二级标题</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>### 三级标题</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>#### 四级标题</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre>##### 五级标题</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"11\"></td><td><pre>###### 六级标题</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214165636751.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"标题效果图\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"二-字体\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#二-字体\">#</a> 二、 字体</h2>\n<p><strong>由 “*” 和 “_” 来控制字体</strong></p>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>粗体<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>__粗体__</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>斜体<span class=\"token operator\">*</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>_斜体_</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span>斜体加粗<span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>___斜体加粗___</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"9\"></td><td><pre></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"10\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">~</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span>删除线<span class=\"token operator\">~</span><span class=\"token operator\">~</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214172259709.png#pic_center\" alt=\"字体效果图\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"三-列表\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#三-列表\">#</a> 三、列表</h2>\n<h4 id=\"1无序列表\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1无序列表\">#</a> 1. 无序列表</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式： <code>*空格</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>无序列表</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> 第一</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> 第二</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> 第三</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">*</span> 第四</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214173533107.png#pic_center\" alt=\"无序列表\" /></p>\n<h4 id=\"2有序列表\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2有序列表\">#</a> 2. 有序列表</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式： <code>数字.空格</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>有序列表</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">1.</span> 第一</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">2.</span> 第二</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">3.</span> 第三</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">4.</span> 第四</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214174138883.png#pic_center\" alt=\"有序列表\" /></p>\n<h4 id=\"3列表嵌套\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#3列表嵌套\">#</a> 3. 列表嵌套</h4>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>列表嵌套</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">1.</span> 第一项：</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.2</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">1.3</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"6\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token number\">2.</span> 第二项：</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"7\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">2.1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"8\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">-</span> <span class=\"token number\">2.2</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214191838670.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"四-分割线\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#四-分割线\">#</a> 四、分割线</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">-</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>    _ _ _</pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span><span class=\"token operator\">*</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214180651652.png#pic_center\" alt=\"分割线\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"五-引用\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#五-引用\">#</a> 五、 引用</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式： <code>&gt;空格</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">2</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">3</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">></span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"5\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">4</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214181327621.png#pic_center\" alt=\"引用\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>引用嵌套</li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">>></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">1.1</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">>>></span> 引用内容<span class=\"token number\">1.1</span><span class=\"token number\">.1</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214181533648.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"六-图片\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#六-图片\">#</a> 六、 图片</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式: <code>![图片名称](图片地址路径)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>本地图片<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>imgs<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>timg<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>png<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>   </pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">!</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>网络图片<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>https<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>ss0<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>bdstatic<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token number\">70</span>cFvHSh_Q1YnxGkpoWK1HF6hhy<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>it<span class=\"token operator\">/</span>u<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">3863286937</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token number\">1191971247</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>fm<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">26</span><span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span>gp<span class=\"token operator\">=</span><span class=\"token number\">0.</span>jpg<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id=\"七-表格\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#七-表格\">#</a> 七、 表格</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式：<br />\n- 头部<br />\n <code>|xxx|xxx|xxx|xxx|</code> <br />\n <code>|--|--|--|--|</code> <br />\n- 内容<br />\n <code>|xxx|xxx|xxx|xxx|</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token operator\">|</span>姓名<span class=\"token operator\">|</span>年龄<span class=\"token operator\">|</span>性别<span class=\"token operator\">|</span>爱好<span class=\"token operator\">|</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token operator\">--</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre>    <span class=\"token operator\">|</span>张三<span class=\"token operator\">|</span><span class=\"token number\">20</span><span class=\"token operator\">|</span>男<span class=\"token operator\">|</span>看电影<span class=\"token operator\">|</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214183926265.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></p>\n<h2 id=\"八-代码块\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#八-代码块\">#</a> 八、 代码块</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>多行：用 “```” 包裹代码块<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214184551734.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70#pic_center\" alt=\"多行代码块\" /></li>\n<li>单行或某个单词<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214184814841.png#pic_center\" alt=\"单行代码块\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"九-超链接\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#九-超链接\">#</a> 九、 超链接</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式： <code>[链接名称](链接地址)</code></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>百度<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>https<span class=\"token operator\">:</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token operator\">/</span>www<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>baidu<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>com<span class=\"token operator\">/</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果：<br />\n<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmFpZHUuY29tLw==\">百度</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"十-目录\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#十-目录\">#</a> 十、 目录</h2>\n<p>自动生成目录</p>\n<ul>\n<li>语法格式： <code>@[toc]</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"十一-其他\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#十一-其他\">#</a> 十一、 其他</h2>\n<figure class=\"highlight java\"><figcaption data-lang=\"java\"></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>上标 <span class=\"token operator\">^</span>上标<span class=\"token operator\">^</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"2\"></td><td><pre> 下标 <span class=\"token operator\">~</span>下标<span class=\"token operator\">~</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"3\"></td><td><pre> 脚注<span class=\"token operator\">^</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>脚注<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span></pre></td></tr><tr><td data-num=\"4\"></td><td><pre> <span class=\"token operator\">==</span>高亮<span class=\"token operator\">==</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214190809568.png#pic_center\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></p>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Other",
                "Markdown"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://lollipopazhe.github.io/2021/08/17/Java/java01/",
            "url": "https://lollipopazhe.github.io/2021/08/17/Java/java01/",
            "title": "Java01-JDK安装及环境变量配置",
            "date_published": "2021-08-17T11:26:32.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"jdk安装及环境变量配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#jdk安装及环境变量配置\">#</a> JDK 安装及环境变量配置</h1>\n<h4 id=\"1找到相应的jdk版本并下载\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#1找到相应的jdk版本并下载\">#</a> 1. 找到相应的 JDK 版本并下载</h4>\n<p>JDK 下载地址：<span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuamRrZG93bmxvYWQuY29tLzIwMjAvMDUvMTYvamRrJWU0JWI4JThiJWU4JWJkJWJkLw==\">https://www.jdkdownload.com/2020/05/16/jdk%e4%b8%8b%e8%bd%bd/</span></p>\n<h4 id=\"2安装过程\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#2安装过程\">#</a> 2. 安装过程</h4>\n<p>选择合适的安装目录（记住这个安装目录，后边配置环境变量要用到），其他步骤一直点下一步即可。</p>\n<h4 id=\"3环境变量配置\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#3环境变量配置\">#</a> 3. 环境变量配置</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>右击 “我的电脑”→属性→高级系统设置→环境变量</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214213213569.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"环境变量1\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>新建环境变量</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214213644726.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>编辑 Path 环境变量（双击）<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214213857969.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /><img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214214245990.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></li>\n<li>全部点 “确定” 退出这些窗口</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"4-检查环境是否配置成功\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#4-检查环境是否配置成功\">#</a> 4、检查环境是否配置成功</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>win+R 打开命令窗口，输入 cmd 后回车打开命令行<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214214733513.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></li>\n<li>在命令行中输入 java -version, 回车若显示 jdk 版本信息则说明安装成功，如下图：<br />\n<img data-src=\"https://img-blog.csdnimg.cn/20201214214936788.png?x-oss-process=image/watermark,type_ZmFuZ3poZW5naGVpdGk,shadow_10,text_aHR0cHM6Ly9ibG9nLmNzZG4ubmV0L3dlaXhpbl80NjE1MjIyNA==,size_16,color_FFFFFF,t_70\" alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" /></li>\n</ul>\n<h6 id=\"至此环境变量已配置完成可以在您的电脑上编写java程序了\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#至此环境变量已配置完成可以在您的电脑上编写java程序了\">#</a> 至此，环境变量已配置完成，可以在您的电脑上编写 Java 程序了。</h6>\n",
            "tags": [
                "Java基础",
                "Java"
            ]
        },
        {
            "id": "https://lollipopazhe.github.io/2021/08/15/hello-world/",
            "url": "https://lollipopazhe.github.io/2021/08/15/hello-world/",
            "title": "Hello World",
            "date_published": "2021-08-15T09:45:41.746Z",
            "content_html": "<p>Welcome to <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvLw==\">Hexo</span>! This is your very first post. Check <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mv\">documentation</span> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3MvdHJvdWJsZXNob290aW5nLmh0bWw=\">troubleshooting</span> or you can ask me on <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9naXRodWIuY29tL2hleG9qcy9oZXhvL2lzc3Vlcw==\">GitHub</span>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"quick-start\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#quick-start\">#</a> Quick Start</h2>\n<h3 id=\"create-a-new-post\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#create-a-new-post\">#</a> Create a new post</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"><span>h</span></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>$ hexo new <span class=\"token string\">\"My New Post\"</span></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvd3JpdGluZy5odG1s\">Writing</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"run-server\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#run-server\">#</a> Run server</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"><span>h</span></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>$ hexo server</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvc2VydmVyLmh0bWw=\">Server</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"generate-static-files\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#generate-static-files\">#</a> Generate static files</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"><span>h</span></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>$ hexo generate</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3MvZ2VuZXJhdGluZy5odG1s\">Generating</span></p>\n<h3 id=\"deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#deploy-to-remote-sites\">#</a> Deploy to remote sites</h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight bash\"><figcaption data-lang=\"bash\"><span>h</span></figcaption><table><tr><td data-num=\"1\"></td><td><pre>$ hexo deploy</pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>More info: <span class=\"exturl\" data-url=\"aHR0cHM6Ly9oZXhvLmlvL2RvY3Mvb25lLWNvbW1hbmQtZGVwbG95bWVudC5odG1s\">Deployment</span></p>\n",
